      <prop type="x-source-segment-count">1</prop>
      <prop type="x-target-segment-count">1</prop>
      <prop type="x-chinese-ref">易經 43 初九</prop>
      <prop type="x-translation-ref">易經 43 初九</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>初九：壯于前趾，往不勝為吝。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>The first NINE, undivided, shows its subject in (the pride of) strength advancing with his toes. He goes forward, but will not succeed. There will be ground for blame.</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
