      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>上六：无號，終有凶。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>The sixth SIX, divided, shows its subject without any (helpers) on whom to call. His end will be evil.</seg>
      </tuv>
